Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:15.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}全てを証明していこう存在していく為の理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:15.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Inside of Kaos I say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:18.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Where can I get the real love and fate，right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:21.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How can I make you know my heart is with you hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.93,0:22:28.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}人間は誰も忘れていく痛めた傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:35.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}時の流れ見送る度に薄れる感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:40.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}たけどこれ以上見過ごしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:41.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Back and forth　心中叫んでやまない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:45.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}time over　消えていく残像それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:50.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:50.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So now that you & I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:53.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I can't live life without you by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:57.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}「I'll believe..」孤独も因縁さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:57.03,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Yeah，yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:00.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}灼熱の記録の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}未来を映すbrightness
